headline: CDW’s Q2 Earnings Call: Our Top 5 Analyst Questions
summary: CDW’s second quarter results reflected positive sales momentum and exceeded Wall Street revenue and profit expectations, yet the market reacted negatively. Management attributed the quarter’s growth to strong demand for hardware upgrades, particularly client devices, and infrastructure projects, bolstered by the Windows 10 end-of-life cycle.
